OL,6,FThieves have targeted five different
OL,7,Fvans in within 10 days, taking items
OL,8,Ffrom three of them.
OL,10,Fsay the first theft happened from a
OL,11,Fsilver Vauxhall Vivaro which was
OL,12,Fparked on the drive of a home near
OL,13,FLytham.
OL,15,FAt some point between 6pm on Saturday
OL,16,F13th January and 9.15am on Monday 15th
OL,17,FJanuary drills and plumbing equipment
OL,18,Fworth #3000 were taken.
