OL,6,FA chainsaw, drill and saws worth more
OL,7,Fthan #1000 were also stolen from a
OL,8,Fsilver Ford Transit which was parked
OL,9,Fat Tamworth Football Club on
OL,10,FKettlebrook Road. Officers believe the
OL,11,Ftheft happened at some point between
OL,12,F4.20pm and 6.15pm on Monday 22nd
OL,13,FJanuary.
OL,15,FOn the same day three vans ` a black
OL,16,FFord Transit, a silver Ford Transit
OL,17,Fand a white Peugeot Partner ` were
OL,18,Fdamaged whilst they were parked at a
OL,19,Fhotel on Bonehill Road, with fishing
OL,20,Fequipment taken from inside one of
OL,21,Fthem.
