OL,6,FStaffordshire Police are investigating
OL,7,Fall the incidents by looking over CCTV
OL,8,Fand patrolling the area proactively.
OL,9,FThey are also urging van owners to be
OL,10,Fvigilant and asking anyone with any
OL,11,Finformation, CCTV or dashcam footage
OL,12,Fto contact them.
OL,14,FChief Inspector Rob Neeson, of the
OL,15,FTamworth local policing team, said:
OL,16,F"We are committed to acting on
OL,17,Fpeople's concerns and taking proactive
OL,18,Faction to stop thieves from taking
OL,19,Fpeople's hard earned belongings.
