OL,6,F"In order to limit the chances of
OL,7,Fbeing targeted by opportunists, we
OL,8,Fadvise people to keep their vehicles
OL,9,Fsecured at all times and kept in clear
OL,10,Fview of CCTV, where possible."
OL,12,F"If you have a secure garage, keep
OL,13,Fyour vehicle inside and consider
OL,14,Finstalling a steering lock as a
OL,15,Ffurther deterrent."
OL,17,F"You should attempt to remove tools
OL,18,Ffrom vans overnight, as thieves will
OL,19,Foften try to target them in night-time
OL,20,Fhours."
